        <updateDate>2013-07-11T20:18:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Transportation for Heroes Act of 2013 - Revises urbanized area formula grant recipient requirements to require a recipient to certify that it will ensure a fare of no more than 50% of the peak hour fare will be charged to a U.S. veteran during non-peak hours for transportation using or involving a facility or equipment of a project financed by the grant.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
